"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the server hashed password of a ResponseHeader.
        """
kwargs = {'server_hashed_password': []}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The server hashed password must be a binary string.', messages.
    ResponseHeader, **kwargs)
args = messages.ResponseHeader(), 'server_hashed_password', []
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The server hashed password must be a binary string.', setattr, *args)
